BEGIN_PGML
Determine if the two lines are the same line, distinct parallel lines, perpendicular lines, or none of the above.

Line [`\ell_1`] contains the points [`[$p[0]]`] and [`[$p[1]]\text{.}`] Line [`\ell_2`] contains the points [`[$p[2]]`] and [`[$p[3]]\text{.}`]

[_]{$choices}{5}

